For other Maven users: this solved the problem.
```
<plugin>
  <groupId>org.scala-tools</groupId>
  <artifactId>maven-scala-plugin</artifactId>
  <configuration>
    <scalaVersion>2.9.0-1</scalaVersion>
    <args>
      <arg>-Xmax-classfile-name</arg>
      <arg>130</arg>
     </args>
  </configuration>
</plugin>
```
